COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 8:53PM PT yesterday, over 1.3 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 18.1 thousand have died.

In the last day, 399 new infections were reported and 11 deaths. Currently 1,265 are in the hospital and 31 are in the ICU. This is trending downwards.

Fortunately, 23.3 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 5 years and older, 31.1% have their 1st shot and 19.7% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is slowing down, but there are -250 thousand doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~102 days for new deliveries to get into arms.

At the current rate, Canadians should achieve herd immunity around when 80% of the entire population is fully vaccinated. There is no approved vaccine for children under 5.
